Importer_MCP
============

Purpose:
- Post-build AI-style quality reviewer for HyImporter outputs.
- Produces natural-language quality notes from deterministic QA metrics.
- Can bridge generated tiles into the bundled `voxelviewer` workspace.

Entry point:
- Python module: `src/hyimporter/importer_mcp.py`

Main commands:
- Review only:
  - `python -m hyimporter.importer_mcp --output-dir <map_out_dir>`
- Review + index in VoxelViewer:
  - `python -m hyimporter.importer_mcp --output-dir <map_out_dir> --index-with-voxelviewer --voxelviewer-root <repo>/voxelviewer`

Output artifacts:
- `<map_out_dir>/qa/importer_mcp_review.json`
- `<map_out_dir>/qa/importer_mcp_review.md`

Helper scripts:
- `scripts/connect_voxelviewer.sh`
- `scripts/connect_voxelviewer.ps1`
